Package cs2030.simulator

Class Server

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030.simulator.Server
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServerID
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HumanServer, SelfCheckOut
    public abstract class Server
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServerID
    This abstract class redirects the service of the customers according to their availability. The status of the server is determined by getting and setting its serving, waiting and resting states.
